snippet: The Collegiate Chorale presented Michael Tippett’s oratorio “A Child of Our Time” and Bruckner’s Te Deum at Carnegie Hall.
abstract: Vivien Schweitzer reviews concert of works by composer Michael Tippett and Anton Bruckner performed by the Collegiate Chorale and the American Symphony Orchestra, conducted by James Bagwell and featuring soprano Nicole Cabell, at Carnegie Hall.
lead_paragraph: The Collegiate Chorale presented Michael Tippett’s oratorio “A Child of Our Time” and Bruckner’s Te Deum at Carnegie Hall.

headline.seo: Collegiate Chorale Sings Tippett and Bruckner at Carnegie
